  <brief_title>Does Perioperative Pregabalin Reduce Postoperative Pain After Arthroscopic Anterior Cruciate Ligament Reconstruction Surgery Under Spinal Anesthesia?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does Perioperative Pregabalin Reduce Postoperative Pain After Arthroscopic Anterior Cruciate Ligament Reconstruction Surgery Under Spinal Anesthesia?</official_title>
